Naggy
=====

Naggy is a product by [Grible](http://grible.co). She's a virtual office manager who removes the hassle of recurring office tasks (watering the plants, cleaning the kitchen, etc). People in your community get text messages whenever a task is assigned to them. Read more on [Naggy's site](http://naggy.co).

Development
-----------
Naggy is a Play Scala project using SBT. Run `activator play-run` or `activator ~play-run` (hot reloading) during development.
